latestIgtvVideos.title: Kasoor
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I remember listening to Prateek Kuhad when I was in love or atleast I thought so because he makes you believe in it. 
From sulking to ‘Go’ while sitting at the airport to pouring my heart out while ‘Tune Kaha’ played in the background. Love songs and all, sad songs for breakups. 
Then came Cold/Mess which stole our hearts and made me fall in love with @jimsarbhforreal too. Lemon tarts from then on got a whole new meaning. 
‘Hopelessly’ had me hopelessly falling in love all over again. ‘Just a word’ had me recalling words unspoken. I remember screaming my lungs out to ‘Khone do’ and swaying to ‘Raat Raazi’. 
Now ‘Kasoor’ is here and although it brought up alot of buried emotions, the video turned out to be amazing.
Thanks for keeping the love alive @prateekkuhad and @jugaadmotionpictures you’ve done such a splendid job with this.
